latestIgtvVideos.title: Mango ice cream 🥭(3 ingredients)
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
for all the mango Lovers🥭 out there 
This recipe came out too delicious and yum and a must try❤️ 

 Ingredients  you need are 
1. Mangoes 5-6 or 2 cups 
2. 3/4 cup condense milk 
3. whipped cream (1.5) cups you can use any brand 
some chopped mangoes are required

. This recipe is super easy to make at home .It doesn't require any extra sugar in it and its perfect. The texture was very creamy & so good

I don't have any copyright of the music its chill by @whydontwemusic ❤️
